hands_on_practices.solution:
我们使用三维抛物线能带，其态密度为 
$$g(E)=A\,E^{1/2},\quad \beta\equiv\frac1{k_BT}.$$
麦克斯韦-玻尔兹曼平均值为
$$\langle A(E)\rangle
=\frac{\int_0^\infty A(E)\,E^{1/2}e^{-\beta E}\,dE}
{\int_0^\infty E^{1/2}e^{-\beta E}\,dE}.$$
1.  平均散射时间：
$$\langle\tau\rangle
=\frac{\int_0^\infty\tau_0E^r\,E^{1/2}e^{-\beta E}\,dE}
{\int_0^\infty E^{1/2}e^{-\beta E}\,dE}
=\tau_0\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac32)\,\beta^{-(r+\tfrac32)}}
{\Gamma(\tfrac32)\,\beta^{-\tfrac32}}
=\tau_0\,(k_BT)^r\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac32)}{\Gamma(\tfrac32)}.$$
因此迁移率为
$$\mu=\frac{q}{m^*}\langle\tau\rangle
=\frac{q\,\tau_0}{m^*}(k_BT)^r\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac32)}{\Gamma(\tfrac32)}.$$
2.  平均扩散系数：
$$D
=\Big\langle\frac13v^2\tau\Big\rangle
=\frac13\frac{\int(2E/m^*)\,\tau_0E^r\,E^{1/2}e^{-\beta E}\,dE}
{\int E^{1/2}e^{-\beta E}\,dE}
=\frac{2\tau_0}{3m^*}\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac52)\,\beta^{-(r+\tfrac52)}}
{\Gamma(\tfrac32)\,\beta^{-\tfrac32}}
=\frac{2\tau_0}{3m^*}(k_BT)^{r+1}\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac52)}{\Gamma(\tfrac32)}.$$
3.  比率和修正因子：
$$\frac{D}{\mu}
=\frac{\displaystyle\frac{2\tau_0}{3m^*}(k_BT)^{r+1}\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac52)}{\Gamma(\tfrac32)}}
{\displaystyle\frac{q\,\tau_0}{m^*}(k_BT)^r\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac32)}{\Gamma(\tfrac32)}}
=\frac{2}{3q}\,k_BT\;\frac{\Gamma(r+\tfrac52)}{\Gamma(r+\tfrac32)}.$$
使用 $\Gamma(r+\tfrac52)=(r+\tfrac32)\,\Gamma(r+\tfrac32)$ 可得
$$\frac{D}{\mu}
=\Bigl(1+\tfrac{2r}{3}\Bigr)\frac{k_BT}{q},$$
所以修正因子为
$$\eta(r)=1+\frac{2r}{3}.$$
